  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "The test was creating two template versions without explicit names, relying on `namesgenerator.NameDigitWith()` which can produce collisions. When both versions got the same random name, the test failed with a 409 Conflict error.\n\nFix by giving each version an explicit name (`v1`, `v2`).\n\nCloses https://github.com/coder/internal/issues/1309\n\n---\n\n*Generated by [mux](https://mux.coder.com)*",
